    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
      <div class="prose max-w-none text-gray-700 space-y-6">
        <p>By using the ROAM Systems website (roamsystems.co.uk), you agree to the following terms and conditions.</p>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mt-8">Use of Website</h2>
        <p>This website is provided for informational purposes and to facilitate product enquiries. You agree to use this website lawfully and in a way that does not infringe upon the rights of others.</p>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mt-8">Products and Pricing</h2>
        <p>All prices shown on our website are in British Pounds (GBP) and are subject to change without notice. Product descriptions and specifications are provided in good faith and are as accurate as possible.</p>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mt-8">Orders</h2>
        <p>Submitting an enquiry through our website does not constitute a binding order. Orders are confirmed once we contact you and payment has been arranged. We reserve the right to refuse any order.</p>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mt-8">Intellectual Property</h2>
